<section class="volunteer" id="volunteer">
	<div class="container">
		<h2 class="align-center">Join the fight!</h2>

		<div class="description">
			<p>Working from home? Want to sharpen your app development skills? Looking for an active way to contribute apart from social distancing or washing your hands?</p>
			<p>Let’s get your hands dirty — virtually. Join any of our workstreams below and volunteer as a tribute.</p>
